title: Bobby’s New Sleeping Technique + Lunchbox Tries To Bribe A Pharmacy + 'Never Gonna Get It' Game!
itunes:title: Bobby’s New Sleeping Technique + Lunchbox Tries To Bribe A Pharmacy + 'Never Gonna Get It' Game!
description:
Bobby shares a new sleeping technique that he’s been using and says has worked every night since! Lunchbox wants to see if a pharmacy will sell him a fake vaccine card if he offers them some money. We play a round of Never Gonna Get It with a hilarious ending.
